The '''Security Officer''' or '''Security Guard''' was the highest ranking group within the [[Royal Naboo Security Forces/Legends|Royal Naboo Security Forces]]. Unfamiliar to true danger, they led the part-time and volunteer members of the [[Law enforcement agency/Legends|security forces]]. Among their ranks is the captain of Security. They roughly numbered over 1,000 before the Clone Wars. They wore a maroon leather jerkin with a blue officers uniform underneath, and their weapon of choice was the [[S-5 heavy blaster pistol/Legends|S-5 heavy blaster pistol]].

